#Zomato Restaurants Analysis Dashboard

##Project Description

An interactive Power BI dashboard built using Zomato restaurant data to analyze restaurant distribution, cuisines, ratings, votes, delivery options, and booking availability across multiple countries and cities.

The dashboard helps understand customer preferences, restaurant performance, and market presence globally.

