ğŸ’¡ Business Insights

India has the highest number of restaurants among all countries.

New Delhi alone contains more than 5,400 restaurants.

North Indian cuisine is the most popular cuisine.

Most restaurants do not support table booking.

Most restaurants offer online delivery.

McDonald's shows the highest average rating among top brands.

Consumer preferences vary strongly by city and cuisine.

(All insights are visible in charts on the dashboard 

overview

)

